From a bird's eye view, a Golden Eagle soared high above the battle 
field of the Predacons.  Though one herself, she had yet to find an 
interest in the battle, until now.  She had been watching the power 
struggle for some time and had now seen which side was stronger.  She 
had been made Pred.  

For years, GoldenEye had stayed in beast mode so as to stay hidden.  
Since her arrival to the planet, she had yet to transform into bot 
mode.  She had lived among the eagles for a long time.  Watching and 
waiting for the factions to show her which one was strong.  It was 
clear that the Predacons of the ship were the stronger faction and 
the one for her to join.  She perched on the top branches of a tree 
and watched.  She would wait until the battle was over and then make 
her move.

Name: GoldenEye
Faction: Predacon
Skills: Fighter, Killer.

Weapons: Talons, Beak, Optic lazars, energon pistol, double barrel 
energon shot gun-sawed off.
